OL,6,FIt's hoped that this bovine
OL,7,Ftraceability should also help to
OL,8,Fprevent the spread of diseases,
OL,9,Fprotecting both animal and public
OL,10,Fhealth.
OL,12,FRobert Neill, a cattle farmer on Upper
OL,13,FNesbit Farm, just outside Jedburgh,
OL,14,Fhas been using electric tags to keep
OL,15,Ftrack of his herd since 2007.
OL,17,F"So low frequency was initially what
OL,18,Fwe started with here, but the, problem
OL,19,Fwith low frequency is the chips are
OL,20,Fnot that big memory can you store a
OL,21,Fcertain amount of numbers.
