OL,6,F"Ultra high frequencies have got more
OL,7,Fcapacity, more memory, you can store
OL,8,Fmedicine records, you can do movements
OL,9,F- the list is endless to what you can
OL,10,Fstore in that tag.
OL,12,F"But we need to mandate this and take
OL,13,Fthe chore of handling and working with
OL,14,Fcattle.
OL,16,FMartin Kennedy from NFU Scotland said
OL,17,Fthey will improve health and safety:
OL,18,F"It's far safer as you can read them
OL,19,Ffrom a distance.
